":[318,520],"id":"dfdc69d6-5750-87b5-620c-5d3d8ffc2325","name":"Note: Extract Structured Fields"},{"parameters":{"content":"### OpenRouter Chat Model\n\nChat model powering the AI step (model: `anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5`). Swap providers here without rewiring.\n\nFeeds **Extract Structured Fields** as `languageModel`\n\n🔑 OpenRouter API key","width":280,"height":232,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[561,1090],"id":"e1eb8f2d-251e-8c9f-a8e0-994a7507a975","name":"Note: OpenRouter Chat Model"},{"parameters":{"content":"### All Required Fields Found?\n\nTwo-way gate on `={{ $json.output?.invoiceNumber }}`. TRUE continues the happy path, FALSE takes the alternate branch.\n\nPorts: ①→ Upsert into Airtable · ②→ Queue for Manual Review","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[885,520],"id":"c1ed3028-0b5b-0a1c-82f0-85aceb6e8d56","name":"Note: All Required Fields Found?"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Upsert into Airtable\n\nairtable — `upsert` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Merge Review Paths · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Airtable PAT","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1209,280],"id":"579609fc-a1bd-17bb-8a6b-b4f819312cd7","name":"Note: Upsert into Airtable"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Queue for Manual Review\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Merge Review Paths · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1533,880],"id":"1e4333f3-cfd7-adc3-da3f-2210e28e2958","name":"Note: Queue for Manual Review"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Merge Review Paths\n\nRejoins 2 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Cap Batch Volume","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2181,520],"id":"92d3ce24-071e-40da-7684-03c01c016b46","name":"Note: Merge Review Paths"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Cap Batch Volume\n\nCaps the stream at 100 items to protect downstream quotas.\n\nNext: Save Execution Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3153,520],"id":"e78d10b2-81c8-6ca2-551e-4907183b73c8","name":"Note: Cap Batch Volume"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Save Execution Metadata\n\nSaves key fields onto the execution record — searchable later in n8n's execution list.\n\nNext: Guard Non-Empty fileName","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3477,520],"id":"67d08ae1-3895-515a-978e-3897910fc2be","name":"Note: Save Execution Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Guard Non-Empty fileName\n\nDrops items that fail the condition; only qualifying items continue (no false branch).\n\nNext: Summarize Run Stats","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3801,520],"id":"cc75d39f-03d5-1ab9-b962-0b40d6e7fa3b","name":"Note: Guard Non-Empty fileName"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Summarize Run Stats\n\nShapes the item: writes `runAt`, `itemCount`, `status`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Append Audit Row (Airtable)","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4125,520],"id":"04e4f4b2-5cb2-6513-8edb-de7dad14256e","name":"Note: Summarize Run Stats"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Append Audit Row (Airtable)\n\nairtable — `create` operation against the connected account.\n\nPorts: ①→ Send Summary to Slack · ②→ Capture Failure Context\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Airtable PAT","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4449,520],"id":"17859f77-170a-4e33-9a6f-1699bfd814e3","name":"Note: Append Audit Row (Airtable)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · ⚠ failures exit via the error rail · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4773,520],"id":"71e20fdf-03db-a974-cfbd-287b7cc320c8","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Capture Failure Context\n\nShapes the item: writes `failedNode`, `errorMessage`, `workflow`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Escalate Failure to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4125,1540],"id":"1c6b1f5a-5a6c-7d95-ded8-4b20e8d1895f","name":"Note: Capture Failure Context"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Escalate Failure to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[4449,1540],"id":"91392c95-c077-4246-181e-ab196fc5fd3e","name":"Note: Escalate Failure to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Digest documents with Airtable and Slack for your team\n\n**Pattern:** AI Summarize & Route · **Level:** Advanced · **Trigger:** Webhook\n\n## What it does\nDigest documents with Airtable and Slack for your team. It fires the moment an external system calls its webhook.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual invoices is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nReceive Inbound Webhook → Collect Raw Text → Extract Structured Fields → All Required Fields Found? → Upsert into Airtable → Merge Review Paths → Cap Batch Volume → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to ai summarize & route without manual effort\n- Anyone automating invoices in legal\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Standardizes the process every time\n- Removes copy-paste errors\n- Keeps your systems in sync\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Airtable PAT; OpenRouter API key; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"6afeb417-62ea-7fd2-05a9-ea819070a122","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛟 Error handling & retries\n\nExternal calls retry **3× with 2s backoff**. Anything still failing exits through its node's error output into the red error rail → context is captured and the on-call channel is alerted. Set an n8n **Error Workflow** in settings as the final safety net.","width":360,"height":260,"color":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-260],"id":"89e6bd7d-b97b-5f2a-6573-a4ce3716db25","name":"🛟 Error handling & retries"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🔐 Security\n\nNever trust inbound payloads: the webhook path is unguessable. Add header auth or IP allow-listing for defense in depth. Secrets live in n8n credentials — never in node parameters.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-260],"id":"d8d26c7d-cfd2-496b-0d94-ff490a382b3e","name":"🔐 Security"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🤖 AI cluster\n\nPurple nodes form one AI unit: the root node orchestrates, sub-nodes plug in via typed ports (model / memory / tools / parser). Swap the chat model without rewiring anything else. Costs scale with tokens — keep prompts lean and cap iterations.","width":360,"height":260,"color":6},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[610,-260],"id":"588ee064-6a87-c051-a55f-98202a76af62","name":"🤖 AI cluster"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your invoices process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1030,-260],"id":"9b072cb1-61cf-dece-720b-ab615a4575b3","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Receive Inbound Webhook":{"main":[[{"node":"Collect Raw Text","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Collect Raw Text":{"main":[[{"node":"Extract Structured Fields","type":"main","index":0}]]},"OpenRouter Chat Model":{"ai_languageModel":[[{"node":"Extract Structured Fields","type":"ai_languageModel","index":0}]]},"Extract Structured Fields":{"main":[[{"node":"All Required Fields Found?","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"All Required Fields Found?":{"main":[[{"node":"Upsert into Airtable","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Queue for Manual Review","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Upsert into Airtable":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Review Paths","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Queue for Manual Review":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Review Paths","type":"main","index":1}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Merge Review Paths":{"main":[[{"node":"Cap Batch Volume","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Cap Batch Volume":{"main":[[{"node":"Save Execution Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Save Execution Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Guard Non-Empty fileName","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Guard Non-Empty fileName":{"main":[[{"node":"Summarize Run Stats","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Summarize Run Stats":{"main":[[{"node":"Append Audit Row (Airtable)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Append Audit Row (Airtable)":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Slack","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Capture Failure Context":{"main":[[{"node":"Escalate Failure to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Send Summary to Slack":{"main":[[],[{"node":"Capture Failure Context","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"dc9dbd54-1351-410d-ae6c-430db6e58f3b","id":"FDX03907"}